languages.text: "Я знал, что мон-кай глупы... но путешествовать меж звезд через владения Сай'лантреш? Я не могу представить себе безумия хуже этого".
"I knew mon-keigh were stupid... but travelling between the stars through the domain of Sai'lanthresh? I cannot imagine a worse kind of madness."

languages.text: “我早就知道猴子很愚蠢……但你们居然在群星之中穿越赛·兰斯雷什的领地？我想象不出比这更疯狂的事情了。”
languages.original_text: "I knew mon-keigh were stupid... but travelling between the stars through the domain of Sai'lanthresh? I cannot imagine a worse kind of madness."

languages.text: « Je savais les mon-keigh stupides... mais pas au point de voyager entre les étoiles dans le domaine même de Sai'lanthresh. Pour ça, il faut être complètement fou. »
languages.original_text: "I knew mon-keigh were stupid... but travelling between the stars through the domain of Sai'lanthresh? I cannot imagine a worse kind of madness."

languages.text: «Sabía que los mon-keigh erais idiotas, pero... ¿viajar entre las estrellas por el dominio de Sai'lanthresh? No se me ocurre mayor locura».

languages.text: 「モン＝ケイは愚かだと思っていたが…セランスレッシュの領域を抜けて星々を旅するとは。ここまで悪い狂気は想像もできなかったぞ」
languages.original_text: "I knew mon-keigh were stupid... but travelling between the stars through the domain of Sai'lanthresh? I cannot imagine a worse kind of madness."

traits.locale_text: 「モン＝ケイは愚かだと思っていたが…セランスレッシュの領域を抜けて星々を旅するとは。ここまで悪い狂気は想像もできなかったぞ」
traits.speaker: MarazhaiCompanion

languages.text: "Ich wusste, dass Chem-Pan-Sey dumm sind ... aber zwischen den Sternen durch das Reich von Sai'lanthresh reisen? Einen schlimmeren Wahnsinn vermag ich mir nicht vorzustellen."
